  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs User A, when User B edits his or her information I want those changes to be reflected in User A's chat/contact/search results for User B.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n\r\n*Summary*: User information isn’t updated on from one user to another, ie User A updates their status/name/picture and then these changes are not updated in User B's information for User A.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nAll User profile information when updated by the user is updated in the UI of all other users\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nProfile updates are not refelcted in the UI of other users\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\nPart One\r\n- Sign in with User A (choose a user)\r\n- Open the fly out menu\r\n- press the \"...\" / more actions button\r\n- Edit Status / Name or Image\r\n- Save changes\r\nPart Two\r\n- Go to another user on different device -> open app, login (choose a different user)\r\n- Search or open chat history with the user from part one\r\n- user profile updates will not be reflected in the UI\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n*Summary*: \r\n\r\n- [ ] ...\r\n- [ ] ...\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Status version: 0.9.12\r\n\r\n* Operating System: iOS 11.2 iPhone SE\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\nn/a",
